Cupid set a record over the threeday 
Valentines Day weekend when 1923 couples purchased wedding 
licenses here 
The figure surpassed last years mark of 1872 licenses 
Valentines weekend is always the biggest weekend of the year 
for the countys Marriage License Bureau 
Over the years liberal marriage laws and the citys festive 
atmosphere have made Las Vegas a marriage capital Each Valentines 
Day the citys two dozen wedding chapels are open for business 24 
hours a day 
The Marriage License Bureau quit counting couples at 5 pm 
Sunday even though the marriages continued through Monday 
